headline: Cboe Global Markets (CBOE): Taking Stock of Valuation After a Strong Multi‑Year Share Price Run
summary: Cboe Global Markets (CBOE) has been quietly grinding higher, with the stock up around 32% over the past year, even as annual revenue slipped and profits inched higher, a mix worth unpacking. See our latest analysis for Cboe Global Markets. With the share price now at $251.83 and a strong year to date share price return of 28.2 percent, Cboe appears to have constructive momentum, supported by a robust 1 year total shareholder return of 31.94 percent and triple digit gains over three and five...
